item.title: About
item.description: Hi. I develop various random things in my spare time. You can follow me on twitter for some exciting content (actually it’s pretty boring). Feel free to check out my games on Google Play Store by searching for “eiby.dev”. If you wish to contact me, just drop me a message at eiby.dev@gmail.com. Cheers!

item.title: Privacy Policy
item.description: Thank you for playing an eiby.dev game. Our games are built as Ad Supported apps. This SERVICE is provided by Eimhin Laverty at no cost and is intended for use as is. This page is used to inform visitors regarding my policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use my Service. If you choose to use my Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this policy.
